response.overview: On February 4th GCW presents Feel No Ways 2024 live on TrillerTV+. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Jack Cartwheel. Also in the lineup:  Tag Team Match Fuego Del Sol & Sam Stackhouse vs Chris Bey & Man Like DeReiss  Mini Abismo Negro vs Microman  Six Man Tag Team Match Deathmatch Royalty (Broski Jimmy, Matt Cardona & Steph De Lander) vs Insane Clown Thrussy (Allie Katch, Dark Sheik & Violent J)  Masha Slamovich vs Starboy Charlie  Six Man Tag Team Match Los Macizos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo) & Rina Yamashita vs Los Desperados (Arez, Gringo Loco & Latigo)  Hammerstone vs Richard Holliday
response.title: GCW: Feel No Ways 2024
